sequenceDiagram
    participant Orchestrator as FMS Guardrails<br/>Orchestrator
    participant Detector as Regex Detector<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Engine as Detection Engine<br/>(detectors.rs)
    participant Kubelet as Kubernetes<br/>Kubelet

    Note over Orchestrator,Engine: Flow 1: PII Detection Request

    Orchestrator->>Detector: POST /api/v1/text/contents<br/>Content-Type: application/json<br/>{ contents: [...], detector_params: { regex: [...] } }
    activate Detector

    Detector->>Engine: Dispatch built-in detectors<br/>(email, ssn, credit-card)
    activate Engine
    Engine-->>Detector: Built-in matches<br/>detection_type: "pii"<br/>score: 1.0
    deactivate Engine

    Detector->>Engine: Dispatch custom regex patterns<br/>(user-supplied patterns)
    activate Engine
    Engine-->>Detector: Custom matches<br/>detection_type: "custom"<br/>score: 1.0
    deactivate Engine

    Detector-->>Orchestrator: 200 OK<br/>JSON array of detections<br/>[{ start, end, text, detection, detection_type, score }]
    deactivate Detector

    Note over Kubelet,Detector: Flow 2: Health Check

    Kubelet->>Detector: GET /health<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    activate Detector
    Detector-->>Kubelet: 200 OK<br/>"healthy"
    deactivate Detector
